This test will make sure the Xubuntu core upgrade will not pull in the xubuntu-desktop meta.
<dl>
    <dt>Install utopic from core.<dt>
    <dt>Make sure xubuntu-desktop isn't installed and uninstall it if it is.<dt>
    <dt>Upgrade to vivid.<dt>
        <dd>Should upgrade without installing a meta.<dd>
</dl>

This test will make sure the a Xubuntu upgrade with no xubuntu-core or xubuntu-desktop will install xubuntu-desktop.
<dl>
    <dt>Install utopic from core.</dt>
    <dt>Make sure both xubuntu-core and xubuntu-desktop aren't installed.</dt>
    <dt>Upgrade to vivid.</dt>
        <dd>This should install xubuntu-core during upgrade.</dd>
</dl>

